Elizabeth Wilson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elizabeth_Wilson 0 Elizabeth Welter Wilson (April 4, 1921 – May 9, 2015) was an American actress whose career spanned nearly 70 years, including memorable roles in film and television. Wilson was inducted into the American Theatre Hall of Fame in 2006.
